            <![endif]--></div><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-height:=
 1.6; color: #15212A;">ACR allows TV makers and other surveillance business=
es to more accurately track watching habits at a far greater scale. Instead=
 of making assessments based on the channel to which an owner=E2=80=99s set=
 is tuned, ACR takes snapshots of audio or video as often as <a href=3D"htt=
ps://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/cc19c638?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315=
f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: =
underline;" target=3D"_blank">every 10 milliseconds</a> from any <a href=3D=
"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/e8578074?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f9=
8315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decorati=
on: underline;" target=3D"_blank">media source connected to your TV</a>, an=
d compares them against a broader video database. Because the technology is=
 built into devices and =E2=80=98consent=E2=80=99 to be tracked is often <a=
 href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/213701e8?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd=
-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-=
decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blank">buried in the terms of service</a=
> required to use smart features, manufacturers and their ACR partners are =
able to track what nearly every smart TV viewer is watching.</p><p style=3D=
"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #15212A;">After a 2017 Feder=
al Trade Commission <a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/a0b9279f?=
m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere;=
 color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blank">complaint</=
a> against Vizio for collecting data without consent,more TV makers have mo=
ved to allow consumers to opt out of ACR tracking.But many don=E2=80=99t ma=
ke it easy.Manufacturers often obscure the software=E2=80=99s invasive natu=
re by naming ACR technology to imply improved user experiences and hiding t=
he <a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/8c796992?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6=
-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; =
text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blank">opt-out option </a><a href=
=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/7d8c749f?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68=
-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decor=
ation: underline;" target=3D"_blank">4-10 clicks</a> into the settings menu=
.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #15212A;">Ev=
en if a user has <a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/7403fe80?m=
=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; =
color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blank">previously o=
pted out</a>, data-sharing permissions are also often <a href=3D"https://fu=
lu-foundation.ghost.io/r/a5c42b7f?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b"=
 style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underli=
ne;" target=3D"_blank">re-enabled </a>during software updates. Those wishin=
g to take more complete measures, such as permanently deleting ACR software=
, risk bricking their device.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-heig=
ht: 1.6; color: #15212A;">As a result, companies gather up to <a href=3D"ht=
tps://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/5d0fba86?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f9831=
5f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration:=
 underline;" target=3D"_blank">100 billion data points</a> each day,which t=
hey use to build advertising profiles about individual viewers that can inc=
lude information such as suspected <a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost=
.io/r/436848bf?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-=
wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_bla=
nk">race, political leanings, </a><a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.=
io/r/43325a15?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-w=
rap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blan=
k">religious beliefs, age,</a> and <a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost=
.io/r/2beab88e?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-=
wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_bla=
nk">geographic location</a><a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/51=
bd5855?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: an=
ywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blank">.</a=
></p><h2 id=3D"tv-makers-are-in-the-surveillance-business-and-business-is-a=
-booming" style=3D"margin-top: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSyste=
mFont, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.11; font-weight=
: 700; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; margin: 1.5em 0 0.5em 0; font-si=
ze: 32px; color: #15212A;">TV makers are in the surveillance business, and =
business is a-booming</h2><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-height: 1.6=
; color: #15212A;">Fueled by ACR data, the connected TV (CTV) advertising b=
usiness is extremely lucrative. <a href=3D"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io=
/r/50750ee4?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wra=
p: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underline;" target=3D"_blank"=
>One estimate</a> predicted the total CTV ad spend to hit $33 billion in 20=
